		<title>原油价格可能在目前水平上锁定低点</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/zh-hans/analysis/market-news/oil-prices-secure-low-at-current-level</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
